#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.value_counts.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.value\\_counts"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:1 of
msgid "Return a Series containing counts of unique values."
msgstr "返回一个包含唯一值计数的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:3 of
msgid ""
"The resulting object will be in descending order so that the first "
"element is the most frequently-occurring element. Excludes NA values by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"结果对象将按降序排列，因此第一个元素是出现频率最高的元素。默认情况下排除 "
"NA 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:7 of
msgid ""
"If True then the object returned will contain the relative frequencies of"
" the unique values."
msgstr "如果为 True，则返回的对象将包含唯一值的相对频率。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:10 of
msgid "Sort by frequencies."
msgstr "按频率排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:12 of
msgid "Sort in ascending order."
msgstr "按升序排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:14 of
msgid ""
"Rather than count values, group them into half-open bins, a convenience "
"for ``pd.cut``, only works with numeric data."
msgstr ""
"不是计算值的计数，而是将它们分组到半开区间中，这是 ``pd.cut`` 的便捷方式"
"，仅适用于数值数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:17 of
msgid "Don't include counts of NaN."
msgstr "不包括 NaN 的计数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:19 of
msgid ""
"'auto', 'shuffle', or 'tree', 'tree' method provide a better performance,"
" while 'shuffle' is recommended if aggregated result is very large, "
"'auto' will use 'shuffle' method in distributed mode and use 'tree' in "
"local mode."
msgstr ""
"'auto'、'shuffle' 或 'tree'，'tree' 方法提供更好的性能，而如果聚合结果"
"非常大，推荐使用 'shuffle'，'auto' 将在分布式模式下使用 'shuffle' 方法，"
"在本地模式下使用 'tree'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.count`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:31 of
msgid "Number of non-NA elements in a Series."
msgstr "Series 中非 NA 元素的数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.count`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:34 of
msgid "Number of non-NA elements in a DataFrame."
msgstr "DataFrame 中非 NA 元素的数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:37 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:48 of
msgid ""
"With `normalize` set to `True`, returns the relative frequency by "
"dividing all values by the sum of values."
msgstr "当 `normalize` 设置为 `True` 时，通过将所有值除以值的总和来返回相对频率。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:59 of
msgid "**dropna**"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.value_counts.value_counts:61 of
msgid "With `dropna` set to `False` we can also see NaN index values."
msgstr "当 `dropna` 设置为 `False` 时，我们也可以看到 NaN 索引值。"

